title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 86-1.5 - Effective period of reimbursement rates
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 86-1.5 - Effective period of reimbursement rates

State Regulations

Certification of reimbursement rates of payment shall be for a 12-month calendar year period or for such other period as may be prescribed by the Commissioner of Health. Notes

York State Register, Volume XXXVI, Issue 27, effective

comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
